<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Phat beimangsa chu ka gel leh,
 Pak bang tuoiin sangmuol a liem;
 Van pak hawih leh nunkhawnuom pen chu,
 Pak bang tuoi ni um puona.

[V2]
 Mu bang ka ngai zuo vang lunlai chu,
 Kum khawsawta Minlun vangkhuo chu;
 Tatte ngabang a lennau vangkhuo,
 Belam No nunnem vangkhuo.

[V3]
 2. Zuo vangkhuo lunlai ka thil leh.
 Ka umna lei pakcha bangin;
 &quot;Kum khawsawta li bang ting ngeilo,
 Ka ngai ie zuo lunlai chu.

[V4]
 3. Lei nawpna leh kipahna hi,
 Naubang kahnan sangmuol aliem;
 Aw van Thagau thelbang thawhsak in,
 Ninnawp tuolthing bang sang ding.

[V5]
 4. Henkawl nang bang Na sut sate
 Pak bang chulin muol a liem ui;
 Aw Lalpa nungtieng sul hei sakin,
 Tanpa zailan awi ung kau.</lyrics>
<title>Sang Muol A Liem !</title>
<hymn_number>194</hymn_number>
</song>